        <mxCell id="p1-iam" value="&lt;b&gt;module.iam_baseline&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;IAM Baseline&#xa;─────────────────&#xa;• Break-glass role (MFA)&#xa;• Password policy (14+ chars)&#xa;• Root account alerts&#xa;• Deny non-MFA API calls&#xa;• IAM Access Analyzer&#xa;• Permission boundary policy" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=8;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
