        <mxCell id="p1-mfa" value="&lt;b&gt;module.mfa_enforcement&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;MFA Enforcement (SCP)&#xa;─────────────────&#xa;• SCP: deny all API w/o MFA&#xa;• Applied: Org root OU&#xa;• Hardware + virtual MFA&#xa;• Controls: NIST IA-2&#xa;  SOC2 CC6.1&#xa;  HIPAA §164.312(d)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=8;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
