        <mxCell id="p1-enhancements" value="Growth-Stage Enhancements vs Baseline&#xa;──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────&#xa;✦ Multi-region active-active (2×VPC, 3 AZs each)&#xa;✦ Cloud WAN attaches both VPCs to workload segment&#xa;✦ Non-prod OU with SCPs (staging / dev separation)&#xa;✦ SCIM 2.0 automated user provisioning from external IdP&#xa;✦ WAFv2: CommonRuleSet + KnownBadInputs + SQLi  (see Page 2)&#xa;✦ Amazon Macie: PII / PHI / PCI discovery in S3  (see Page 2)&#xa;✦ AWS Config Aggregator: org-wide, all-regions  (see Page 2)&#xa;✦ Dual compliance standard: SOC 2 Type II + HIPAA  (see Page 2)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#d79b00;fillColor=#fffde7;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=10;rounded=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
